These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, milk, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
City: rome, liverpool, san-francisco, prague
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is the person drinking milk##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the fan of techno##2
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the rat##1
11. the fan of funk is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | milk  | hot-chocolate    | coffee    | soy-milk   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| City   | liverpool | rome | prague    | san-francisco |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

