.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, bus, motorbike, snowmobile
City: venice, prague, colone, san-francisco
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Transport   | motorbike | tram   | bus   | snowmobile    |
| City         | colone | san-francisco  | venice | prague   |

