.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
City: colone, san-francisco, rome, marseilles
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, tiparillo, dannemann, pall-mall
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 2. the egyptian is the dannemann-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 4. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the italian##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the british##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| City      | colone | rome   | marseilles    | san-francisco      |
| Cigar           | dannemann | baccarat | tiparillo | pall-mall     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

