.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, action, western
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, indonesian, indian, australian
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person eating corn##1
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the indian##3
 4. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the australian##1
 6. the indian is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the indian##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the indian is the person watching spy movies##1
10. the turkish is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| Movie-Genre      | western | spy    | action  | time-travel |
| Nationality      | indonesian  | indian  | turkish | australian    |

