.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, ferret, chinchilla
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku
House: craftsman, cottage, wooden, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 3. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the cottage house is the owner of the dog##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the frog is the craftsman house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the cottage house##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Pet    | ferret    | chinchilla      | dog          | frog    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | sudoku       | rock-climbing | gardening |
| House     | farmhouse     | wooden      | cottage     | craftsman |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

