.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, november, may
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cauliflower, orange
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, folk, gospel
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, quad-bike, bus
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of gospel is between the person driving the quad-bike and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of folk is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday      | november  | january    | february       | may       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | folk        | gospel    | dubstep   |
| Transport   | train  | quad-bike      | bus    | ship |

