There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, hot-chocolate, water
 1. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking water and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
