.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
House: futuristic, craftsman, wooden, townhouse
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, emerald, apricot, amber
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person who likes amber is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| House      | wooden       | craftsman | futuristic        | townhouse        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Color   | amber     | emerald        | fuchsia    | apricot      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

