.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, purple, white, brown
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, april, may
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person who likes brown is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the french##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person who likes purple is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | purple      | lavender | brown     | white        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| Birthday         | october    | september | april      | may |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 